               <item n="m_remarks_old">&lt;p&gt;Complete left part of a leaf with the string hole, PK NS 350 makes a perfect joint on the right side. In the first line of the verso side material from another fragment seems to have been glued over the writing in some cases, which makes the reading difficult.&lt;/p&gt;
